cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use gpu-monitor in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "gpu-monitor"
abstract: >
  A lightweight, single-file NVIDIA GPU monitor with zero dependencies.
  Supports 15 notification channels (Slack, Discord, Telegram, Email, SMS,
  WeCom, Feishu, DingTalk, Bark, ntfy, Gotify, Pushover, Microsoft Teams,
  OpenClaw, iMessage), Prometheus metrics, process crash detection, and a
  real-time GitHub Pages dashboard for multi-machine setups.
authors:
